 * File: [Admin System] Product Catalog Export Tool
 * Template Name: [Admin System] Product Catalog Export Tool
 * Shortcode: (none — REST-only)
 * Version: V.1.3 — disable floating "Export Catalog (ZIP)" button (migration complete, clutter).
 *   REST endpoints /wp-json/dinoco-export/v1/* still active — admin can still export via direct URL
 *   (POST /wp-json/dinoco-export/v1/download-all with WP nonce). Re-enable button: uncomment
 *   add_action('wp_footer', 'dinoco_export_inject_button', 99) in file.
 * Version: V.1.2 — Phase 1: include migration-audit-report-YYYYMMDD.csv in ZIP bundle (5 files → 6 files)
 * Previous: V.1.1 — Add /download-all ZIP endpoint (1-click UX, no curl/secret needed) + inline UI button
 * DB_ID: (auto-assigned by WP after sync)
 * Author: DINOCO Tech Lead
 *
 * PURPOSE
 *   Baseline export ของ Product Catalog state ก่อนเปลี่ยน B2F maker architecture
 *   ให้ทีม review ข้อมูลจริงก่อน decide (Option A vs C vs F)
 *
 * SCOPE
 *   - ทุก SKU ใน wp_dinoco_products (ประมาณ ~153 rows)
 *   - sku_relations (parent → children map)
 *   - per-maker b2f_maker_product CPT (unit_cost, moq, lead_time, shipping, status)
 *
 * ENDPOINTS (namespace: dinoco-export/v1)
 *   GET /wp-json/dinoco-export/v1/catalog?format=json|csv|tree&key=SECRET
 *   GET /wp-json/dinoco-export/v1/makers?format=csv&key=SECRET
 *   GET /wp-json/dinoco-export/v1/download-all   (V.1.2 — admin-only, ZIP w/ 5 files including migration audit, no secret)
 *   GET /wp-json/dinoco-export/v1/health
 *
 * AUTH
 *   - ถ้า user logged-in + manage_options → pass
 *   - ถ้าไม่ → ต้องส่ง ?key=<SECRET>
 *     SECRET = constant DINOCO_EXPORT_KEY (ถ้า define) หรือ auto-gen wp_option 'dinoco_export_key' (32 bytes)
 *   - rate limit 20 req/hour per IP (transient) สำหรับ endpoints ที่รับ secret key
 *   - /download-all = admin-only + rate limit 5 req/hour/user (transient per user_id)
 *
 * SECURITY NOTES
 *   - cost data (mp_unit_cost) = confidential — auth บังคับ
 *   - secret key rotate ได้ผ่าน GET /health?rotate=1 (admin only)
 *   - Content-Disposition: attachment → browser download
 *   - ข้อมูลทั้งหมดส่งผ่าน HTTPS (WP config บังคับ)
 *   - /download-all ไม่ใช้ secret key → admin session + capability check เท่านั้น (UX-friendly)
 */

